<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>829</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>shén jì niàn wǒ men 迦南829</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén méi yǒu jì niàn zhōng guó de zhǎng chéng,
 yě bù jì niàn rén shì jiān yǒu duō shǎo yīng xióng.
 tā què kàn wǒ men wèi bǎo guì.
 jì niàn wèi zhe tā shòu kǔ de bǎi xìng.
 wǒ men hé děng yǒu fú a, wǒ men hé děng yǒu zūn róng.
 wǒ men shì shén téng ài de ér nǚ, fù cháng jì zài xīn zhōng.
 shì jiè kàn wǒ men rú fèi qì de shí tóu,
 shén què jiǎn xuǎn wǒ men lái jiàn zào chéng wèi líng gōng.
 wǒ men hé děng yǒu fú a, wǒ men hé děng yǒu zūn róng.
 wǒ men shì shén téng ài de ér nǚ, zài zhōng guó de jiàn zhèng.</lyrics>
</song>